text: Marius Mocanu (born 9 December 1986) is a Romanian handballer who plays for HC Dobrogea Sud Constanța and the Romania national team. ==Achievements== *Liga Națională: **Winner: 2010, 2011, 2016, 2017, 2018 **The Romanian Cup 2017 **The Supercup 2017 **Bronze 2015 **Silver 2019 ==Individual awards== *All- Star Pivot of the Liga Națională: 2017, 2018 ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:People from Călărași Category:Romanian male handball players Category:HC Dobrogea Sud Constanța players Category:CS Dinamo București (men's handball) players
title: Marius Mocanu
